  "title": "Landscape Worker/ Gardener",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintenance of plants, shrubs,      trees, flowerbed, grass turfs, irrigation system.</li>\n  <li>Application of fertilizer,      pesticide and other chemicals that will promote the growth of the plants.</li>\n  <li>Watering of plants and removal of      weeds or unwanted plants.</li>\n  <li>Cutting or pruning of plants.</li>\n  <li>Plant propagation.</li>\n  <li>Communicate with team leaders      about any potential job risk/hazard</li>\n  <li>Perform other instructions from      the Landscape Supervisor and Manager.</li>\n  <li>Any duties as assigned by      immediate superior/management.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Primary/Secondary/’O’ Level      Education with relevant landscape gardening experience.</li>\n  <li>With WSQ Landscape Operation      (Entry Level) Certification will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>No age limit with ability to work      outdoors.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit to handle tools      and move around easily during work.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Others Information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Salary Negotiable</li>\n  <li>Singaporean preferred</li>\n</ul>",
